===Light novels===
The first light novel volume was published by [[Fujimi Shobo]] under their [[Fujimi Fantasia Bunko]] imprint on July 20, 2012. As of October 2017, thirteen volumes and one short story collection have been published. In the twelfth volume, Maruto announced that the series would end in the thirteenth volume,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-03-17/how-to-raise-a-boring-girlfriend-light-novel-series-ends-in-13th-volume/.113592|title=How to Raise A Boring Girlfriend Light Novel Series Ends in 13th Volume|date=March 18, 2017|website=[[Anime News Network]]|accessdate=March 18, 2017}}</ref> which was released on October 20, 2017.<ref name="FinalLN"/>

